{"tid":833345,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【節目播內地客被警抬離酒店事件】 【中國譴責瑞典電視台：言論惡毒、辱華】","createTime":"2018-09-23T12:31:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-23T16:24:45.000Z","uid":73092,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e356bcdb509a679c4a7de5eb1fbb6a290f7268c1","tid":833345,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T12:31:17.000Z","msg":"【節目播內地客被警抬離酒店事件】<br />\n【中國譴責瑞典電視台：言論惡毒、辱華】<br />\n<br />\n內地遊客被瑞典警察抬離酒店風波持續。<br />\n<br />\n瑞典電視台播放節目討論事件，中國駐瑞典大使館強烈譴責節目辱華。<br />\n<br />\n瑞典電視台上周五播放節目「瑞典新聞」，主持人嘲諷內地遊客被瑞典警察抬離酒店，節目又影射中國人隨處便溺。<br />\n<br />\n中國駐瑞典大使館批評，主持人言論惡毒、侮辱、攻擊中國，赤裸裸散播種族主義和排外主義，煽動針對中國及其他族裔的種族仇視。<br />\n<br />\n批評電視台，突破人類道德底線。<br />\n<br />\n中國大使館又指，節目使用的中國地圖缺少台灣及西藏部分地區，嚴重侵犯中國主權和領土完整。<br />\n<br />\n瑞典電視台回應，這是娛樂節目。<br />\n<br />\n但中方指不能接受，敦促對方立即道歉，並保留採取進一步措施權利。<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/685915548447102/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fvideos%2F685915548447102%2F&d=%2FMEdkqc0cln%2BOwrtBk92tOPnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=b89cab56\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/685915548447102/</a>"},{"pid":"bf18f7649e97838bf794271a6b7cac125053b76a","tid":833345,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T12:32:01.000Z","msg":"k拿<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef249f87c21b24d6343435492b7ea46cb89a84a2","tid":833345,"uid":109743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T14:53:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3883c895c3cbf0925c7d9da7475f8209346c592d","tid":833345,"uid":75521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T15:52:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\"